<body>
<!-- insert navbar via ejs-->
<%- include('./partials/navbar') %>

<!-- Background image and text -->
<section id="background">
    <div class="container-fluid text-center" style="margin-bottom:0">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 background-title">
                <h1>SaberChat</h1>
                <p>Welcome to SaberChat, Alsion's very own communication platform!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Home Page content -->
<section>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 5rem;">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h1>About</h1>
                <p>SaberChat is a platform that connects and centralizes Alsion's various communication and notification platforms, streamlining communication between students, teachers, parents and more.</p>
                <p>Users can quickly access any important information from teachers, communicate with others, and access some of Alsion's unique projects.</p>
                <p>Centralizing our school's content to an inclusive platform will improve our school's identity, as well as relationships between students, parents and teachers across the school.</p>
                <em><strong>Developers: </strong>Alexander Zhou, Kabir Samsi, Siddharth Chavan, Vibhav Darsha</em>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/BmLCEgeCAAAmESz.jpg:large" alt="Our community">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 5rem;">
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                <h1>Services</h1>
                <ul>
                  <li>Chat rooms for students and teachers</li>
                  <li>A bulletin where teachers can post important announcements</li>
                  <li>A more efficient ordering system for Early College's No Left Turn Cafe, which allows students to order online and receive status updates on their orders</li>
                  <li>Access to Alsion's online magazine, Witherly Heights</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <!-- <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1593441259108-980416c4fda3?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2089&q=80" alt="fancy pic"> -->
                <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/BmLCEgeCAAAmESz.jpg:large" alt="Our community">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 5rem;">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h1>Community</h1>
                <p>SaberChat reaches out to all of our community members - students, teachers and parents in both Early College and Middle School. As members of a small, tight-nit school, we value our community deeply.
                  SaberChat will strengthen the relationships between every Alsionite.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/BmLCEgeCAAAmESz.jpg:large" alt="Our community">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
